sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:9:| CC-002 | Tune a per-voice reverb on each FX bus to match its space description in `cypherclaw-v2-design-statement-2026-05-22.md` §4. | MUST | T2 |  |
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:10:| CC-003 | Route per-voice audio into the matching FX bus via the `fx_bus_id` parameter on each voice synthdef. | MUST | T1 |  |
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:11:| CC-004 | Implement mood-driven space selection per scene: matched (default), expressive (deliberate mismatch), house-bound (all voices share the active house's space). | MUST | T2 |  |
