sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:50:| CC-061 | Each voice provides internal LFOs (vibrato pitch LFO, tremolo amplitude LFO, spectral granulation) where allowed by the voice's gesture allowlist. | MUST | T2 |  |
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:52:| CC-063 | The voice-to-gesture allowlist per `cypherclaw-v2-design-statement-2026-05-22.md` §7.3 is enforced; forbidden combinations are rejected. | MUST | T1 |  |
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:54:| CC-065 | Pedal logic (Sustain, Resonant with Decay Modulation, Half-pedal) is implemented per voice family. | MUST | T2 |  |
sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/requirements-register.md:59:| CC-070 | Provision an `affective_state_bus` SuperCollider control bus shared across voices. | MUST | T1 |  |
