y the functionality and the redaction specifically.\n\n## Issues Found\n- None.\n\n## Verdict: PASS\n\n## Notes for Lead Agent\nThe implementation is solid. The use of `_redact_command_output` provides good protection against accidental secret leakage in replay logs.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-038 @20260515t214233z-verify.md"}}
