+   range.
+   VERIFY: `pytest tests/test_senseweave_voice.py::TestAffectiveStateBusReader::test_reader_clamps_bus_values_when_coupling_enabled -q`
+
+4. Existing affective-bus writer, flag, and decay behavior remain green.
